data.description:
Seller will credit buyer $10,000 at closing towards closing costs or interest rate buy down!
Welcome to this charming 1920s gem located in downtown Kalispell. This updated home seamlessly blends the character of a bygone era with modern upgrades. This property offers a unique opportunity to own a piece of history in a sought-after neighborhood, conveniently located near Flathead High School and Russell Elementary. shopping, and restaurants.  This 4-bedroom, 2 bath home boasts a spacious lower level floor plan, providing ample space for comfortable living. Primary Bedroom on Main level. Large mud room, wood stove, wood floors, and even a Chicken coup and Green house. Imagine enjoying mornings on the front porch or relaxing in the backyard, all while being a part of a friendly and welcoming community. Don't miss the chance to make this wonderful house your new home. Call Gabriel Broughton at 406-890-4601 or your real estate professional to schedule a showing.
